Priority / Implementation Order
#	Feature	Effort	Value
E	Named rules {name=...}	Low	Prerequisite for all others
B	History buffer {history=N}	Low	High — no CSP changes needed
C	er.info() inspector	Low	High — data already available
A	Sub-expression trace {trace=true}	Medium	Very high — addresses #1 pain point
D	er.watch() live toggle	Low (needs A)	High
F	plua desktop panel	High	High for plua-only dev workflow

Start with E → B → C as they require no compiler changes.
A is the big win and the prerequisite for D.